Title: Part 3: A long Journey
Text:
Elrond the Lord of the Elves has decided in his council that the Ring of Power must be destroyed!

But this is only possible in Mount Doom in Mordor!

The journey takes me next to the Mines of Moria.

The entrance is in Eregion at the West Gate.
CompleteText:
Here it should be, the west gate of Moria.
The secret door is only revealed in the moonlight.

There is Gandalf. I should talk to him.
